# =============================================================================
# META-STAMP V3 Frontend Environment Configuration Template
# =============================================================================
#
# IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTICE:
# --------------------------
# This file is a TEMPLATE ONLY. Never commit actual secrets or credentials!
#
# To use this file:
# 1. Copy this file to .env in the same directory: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Update the values in .env with your actual configuration
# 3. The .env file is gitignored and should NEVER be committed to version control
#
